'''P1-DK''' was a [[Maintenance droid/Legends|maintenance droid]] in the Sub-levels of the [[Telos IV]] military base in the aftermath of the [[Jedi Civil War]]. P1-DK was reactivated by [[HK-47]] during his attack on the [[HK Factory]]. P1-DK operated on HK-47s self-preservation program to allow him to stop being one of the HK-50 units, allowing him to attack and harm the duplicates.

